There are other formats and tools to define and install package dependencies. Create an app directory and enter it.
Create an empty file __init__.py.
Create a main.py file with: from fastapi import FastAPI app = FastAPI() @app.get("/") def read_root(): return {"Hello": "World"} @app.get("/items/{item_id}") def read_item(item_id: int, q: str | None = None): return {"item_id": item_id, "q": q}
